Package: ken
Type: Package
Title: Kobo Data Cleaning and Quality Assurance
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("M.", "Azemi", email = "mazemi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides comprehensive data cleaning, validation, and quality assurance tools
    for Kobo Toolbox survey data. Includes functions for downloading data from Kobo,
    audit log processing, geographic validation, time checks, outlier detection,
    and automated data quality reporting. Designed for humanitarian and development
    sector data cleaning workflows.
